This paper deals with deep neural networks and their training, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus is on improving the transfer of knowledge from a teacher network to a student network, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.NE). The use of singular value decomposition (SVD) is a mathematical technique that is often used in data analysis and dimensionality reduction, which is relevant to the field of data science (cs.DS).
